\newlabel{fig:lowexc_omegarhoeg}{{4.4}{22}{Left: $|\Omega |^2$, right: $|\rho _{eg}|^2$ is plotted for different excitations, ranging from pulse area $\mathcal {A} = 0 \pi $ to $0.012 \pi $. Always the last slices were plotted. The colorbar shows the intensity in arbitrary units \relax }{figure.caption.11}{}}
