\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.5}{\ignorespaces The ratio $|\rho _{eg}|^2 / \rho _{ee}$ is plotted for different excitations, ranging from pulse area $\mathcal  {A} = 0 \pi $ to $0.012 \tmspace  +\thickmuskip {.2777em}\pi $. The slices 5, 200, 400 are plotted out of the total number of slices $N = 400$. The colorbar shows the intensity in arbitrary units. \relax }}{23}{figure.caption.12}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:lowexc_ratio}{{4.5}{23}{The ratio $|\rho _{eg}|^2 / \rho _{ee}$ is plotted for different excitations, ranging from pulse area $\mathcal {A} = 0 \pi $ to $0.012 \;\pi $. The slices 5, 200, 400 are plotted out of the total number of slices $N = 400$. The colorbar shows the intensity in arbitrary units. \relax }{figure.caption.12}{}}
